HowHardCoultItBe (HHCIB) project. A web application where people can submit their way of craftmanship things such as 'How to build a swimming pool foundation', 'Preparing a Lobster' 
or 'How making a certain tax reduction'. HHCIB also includes a voting mechanism. 

